fun mom dinner is a 2017 american comedy film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; jones , from a screenplay by julie rudd . it stars katie aselton , toni collette , bridget everett , molly shannon , adam scott and adam levine . the film had its world premiere at the sundance film festival on january 27 , 2017 . it was released on august 4 , 2017 by momentum pictures .